title: FedEx 's revenue 2009 to 2019
summary: In general Revenue in billion U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Revenue in billion U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2009 to 2010, slightly increasing from 2010 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2015, and lastly slightly increasing from 2015 to 2017.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Revenue in billion U.S. dollars, about 60.32 was reported at Year 2017
The lowest Revenue in billion U.S. dollars, of value 34.73 was reported at Year 2010
